title: Stop Holding On To What Holds You Back
itunes:title: Stop Holding On To What Holds You Back
description:
Episode 270 - People view their past and their problems as a badge of honor. They lived through it, so they want to carry it with them proudly. The only problem with that is that it holds them back from their true potential. Listen to this episode to learn how to get past the things that are holding you back from your greatness.
